@startuml SSD_RegisterEmployee
title SSD: UC4 - Register Employee

actor "Center Administrator" as Admin
participant ":System" as System

autonumber

activate Admin
Admin -> System: starts the registration of a new employee
activate System
System --> Admin: shows the available roles (Nurse, Receptionist) and asks to select one
deactivate System

Admin -> System: selects the intended role
activate System
System --> Admin: requests the remaining employee's information (id, name, address, phone, email, citizen card number)
deactivate System

Admin -> System: inputs the requested data
activate System
System --> Admin: shows the inputted data and requests confirmation
deactivate System

Admin -> System: confirms the data
activate System
System --> Admin: validates data, registers the employee and informs success
deactivate System
deactivate Admin

@enduml